{"tid":496942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我話親手畫聖誕卡俾你地，唔知有無人要呢？","createTime":"2017-12-12T08:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T22:25:24.000Z","uid":156646,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a550dd7f400730e25666a72257b4a9fc5bb11bfd","tid":496942,"uid":156646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"臨近聖誕<br />\n小弟想送下自己畫既聖誕卡俾大家，送上一點祝福同溫暖<br />\n畫技都唔太差既 <br />\n唔知有無人想要？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於小弟仲讀緊書遲啲開sem會開始忙，所以名額有限，就定50個啦<br />\n<br />\n最遲19號寄出，咁18號截止啦<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係之前畫既，但唔會畫到咁難，因為要畫好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以各位唔好太大期望啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/142818_a64e8f8fb16454390ea77027cae9b2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F142818_a64e8f8fb16454390ea77027cae9b2d4.jpg&h=3e379fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/142819_f0458735e3a001e978ddb503785d7268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F142819_f0458735e3a001e978ddb503785d7268.jpg&h=02f34fae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/142820_f0458735e3a001e978ddb503785d7268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F142820_f0458735e3a001e978ddb503785d7268.jpg&h=ffa7c870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想要既就 tg 我，寫低你想寄去既地址同埋收信人既名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fmlmao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffmlmao&d=yp2e5tveSbr5S2cn2sXZ149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2d9af15d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fmlmao</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個好小好小既要求，如果收到信既絲打巴打可以自行選擇post張卡上黎報平安，同埋留低一兩句祝福既說話送俾大家。<br />\n<br />\n希望今個聖誕大家可以因爲我一封小小既信而開心同感到溫暖！"},{"pid":"1b3f250dc2954f29cc6e2684f2a8b1b2860352e4","tid":496942,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"好有意義 幫你pish"},{"pid":"712ecd1e5965a3714d3f596bda404d6cdcc8100f","tid":496942,"uid":153440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"8ba0f92932d8396a71073b3a3cedcce3d672239f","tid":496942,"uid":142004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"想要！！"},{"pid":"05715321e2b9787abcf547811fd75a91825a42fe","tid":496942,"uid":151309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已tg"},{"pid":"582c36ec9fed2f6077609cb6d68d4aae5bceaab2","tid":496942,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d917e6030e3d2c9b7c0e1c3ab475c09f24d45b","tid":496942,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3e0a6dccf0902a471a17761a714511bbcf5041c7","tid":496942,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"人在外國....介唔介意寄埋俾我架....."},{"pid":"9aee7f49e349073936c305834de6d7dfec717dbc","tid":496942,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5785a2bae96d4837f34ed7c62bf790d057ef0ed9","tid":496942,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"淨係識俾女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8079c414732b081527519b3dc3d3f749197aae82","tid